    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in truly pristine condition\u2014not a scratch or a dent in sight! I\u2019m honestly sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been meticulously cared for and is ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
