    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. This example is mechanically flawless, having received documented VAC Motorsports rod bearing replacements and a full Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul. The chassis is reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points, ensuring structural rigidity under high-lateral G loads. Power is managed by a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The exterior retains its original factory-spec paint depth, and the cabin is pristine with zero bolster wear on the Nappa leather. A turn-key masterpiece for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
