      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, having been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and scent-free, with every button and digital display functioning exactly as they did on the delivery floor. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, backed by a complete, documented service history and exceptionally low mileage. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched factory floor mats, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. It comes complete with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title. For the buyer who demands perfection, this is the one.",
