    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to be passing this beauty along to a new home. It\u2019s in absolutely flawless condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken incredibly good care of it, so there isn\u2019t a single scratch or speck of dust to be found. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I know you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come see it in person and take it for a spin!",
